  "response": "While I don't have real-time data or specific recruitment practices of Bridgehampton National Bank, organizations typically seek candidates from universities that have strong programs in business, finance, economics, or related fields. Common majors that banks and financial institutions often look for include:\n\n- Finance\n- Accounting\n- Business Administration\n- Economics\n- Marketing\n- Management\n- Mathematics or Statistics\n\nTo find specific universities that Bridgehampton National Bank recruits from or to see their latest recruitment trends, I recommend checking their official website, their career page, or reaching out to their HR department directly. Networking platforms like LinkedIn can also provide insights into which universities their employees graduated from. Additionally, attending job fairs or industry events can help you gather information on their recruiting practices.",
